00:08:21,795 --> 00:08:24,616
Everyone working on a specific project is clustered together,

145
00:08:24,696 --> 00:08:26,496
regardless of what they do on that project.

146
00:08:27,137 --> 00:08:29,517
In the departmental layout, artists sit with artists,

147
00:08:29,557 --> 00:08:32,078
producers sit with the producers, design sits over there,

148
00:08:32,158 --> 00:08:34,459
engineers sit over there, even if there are two or three

149
00:08:34,499 --> 00:08:35,819
different games that they're working on.

150
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:38,340
