153
00:08:41,921 --> 00:08:44,062
you don't have to go too far to find and collaborate

154
00:08:44,102 --> 00:08:45,223
with the other devs who are working

155
00:08:45,263 --> 00:08:46,643
on the same problems as you are.

156
00:08:47,383 --> 00:08:48,984
As we know from those factory studies 100 years ago,

157
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:52,581
the less you have to physically move to get your job done,

158
00:08:52,861 --> 00:08:54,622
the more efficient you're going to be at doing it.

159
00:08:54,642 --> 00:08:56,502
