00:26:43,493 --> 00:26:48,736
Engineers do not have the same requirements as designers or artists or marketers.

494
00:26:49,236 --> 00:26:53,078
If you have one type of space for all of these different types of folks, you're setting yourself

495
00:26:53,138 --> 00:26:54,339
up for a big challenge.

496
00:26:54,859 --> 00:26:59,102
Even in a small studio, you have to do what you can to make sure that there's quiet space

497
00:26:59,222 --> 00:27:03,764
and collaboration space available and that they're as distinct and distant physically

