00:27:12,039 --> 00:27:17,783
in the survey, but close behind it were a few different types of issues around privacy.

501
00:27:18,244 --> 00:27:23,488
Physical privacy and visual privacy are separate, and they're both very important. Game developers,

502
00:27:23,528 --> 00:27:26,991
