507
00:27:44,827 --> 00:27:45,668
they're going to get fired.

508
00:27:46,949 --> 00:27:50,353
There are better ways to find out if your employees are shirking their responsibilities

509
00:27:50,393 --> 00:27:52,896
than by fixing all their screens towards the boss.

510
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:59,023
is an important and enormous part of what we do.

